{"tid":1154912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子幫狗隻取名「城管」　涉尋釁滋事被拘留10日","createTime":"2019-05-14T15:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T10:21:32.000Z","uid":133680,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b206afe4c912ebb20c9a512f80f1afe4934cb7e8","tid":1154912,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T15:10:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190514/mobile/bkn-20190514180608717-0514_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190514%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190514180608717-0514_00952_001.html&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZwx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=7a1634e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190514/mobile/bkn-20190514180608717-0514_00952_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n兩岸新聞<br />\n<br />\n男子幫狗隻取名「城管」 涉尋釁滋事被拘留10日<br />\n05月14日(二) 18:24更新 18:06建立   <br />\n更多新聞短片<br />\n<br />\n許多人都會按自己喜好為貓狗改名，原來這些在內地都有限制。安徽阜陽一名班姓男子，將自己養的狗稱作「城管」、「協管」，結果遭到舉報，被警方傳召及行拘了10日。 <br />\n<br />\n班某在微信朋友圈上發布多張黑色狗隻的照片，配文寫道：「曝光兩張城管照片」、「來一組協管的放大鏡頭」；他又上傳一段狗隻趴在地上的影片，稱「城管吃了就知道睡」。 <br />\n<br />\n警方通報，班某從事狗隻販賣的生意。他自稱為狗隻取上述名字，純粹是覺得好玩，不知已違反法例。警方研究後，以涉尋釁滋事對他作出上述處罰，目前已送阜陽市拘留所執行。"},{"pid":"f2cbc630c860dea477fda1a0c60fc45102fde49d","tid":1154912,"uid":150301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T15:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b02078be7b10962177cc70f799b0cf7a66bb52","tid":1154912,"uid":3510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T15:12:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾過癮"},{"pid":"b75bee06e20dafc83d004c45f7ff1a096b5f4ae8","tid":1154912,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T15:12:29.000Z","msg":"政府搞鳩人民萬能key"},{"pid":"67